<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1015,1294]" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,368,1195,1221]" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">Identification.</emphasis>
This species was identified from descriptions and illustrations found in the revision by 
<bibRefCitation author="Prather, A. L." pageId="2" pageNumber="580" pagination="1 - 76" refId="ref6469" refString="Prather, A. L. (2004) Revision of the Neotropical caddisfly genus Banyallarga (Trichoptera: Calamoceratidae). Zootaxa, 435 (1), 1 - 76. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 435.1.1" type="journal article" year="2004">Prather (2004)</bibRefCitation>
. It is similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Prather Table Of Contents" authorityYear="2004" box="[412,555,1231,1257]" class="Insecta" family="Calamoceratidae" genus="Banyallarga" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="580" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quincemil">
<emphasis box="[412,555,1231,1257]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">B. quincemil</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="AL Prather" authorityYear="2004" box="[613,732,1231,1257]" class="Insecta" family="Calamoceratidae" genus="Banyallarga" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="580" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sylvana">
<emphasis box="[613,732,1231,1257]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">B. sylvana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but differs in having a long, acute apicoventral projection of tergum X.
</paragraph>
